Suppose we have a collection called `customers` with the following documents:

```json
[
  {
    "_id": 1,
    "name": "John Doe",
    "email": "john@example.com",
    "phone": "123-456-7890"
  },
  {
    "_id": 2,
    "name": "Jane Doe",
    "email": "jane@example.com",
    "phone": "098-765-4321"
  },
  {
    "_id": 3,
    "name": "Bob Smith",
    "email": "bob@example.com"
  }
]
```

Running the query would return the following results:

```json
[
  {
    "_id": null,
    "count": 2
  },
  {
    "_id": "name",
    "dataTypes": [
      { "type": "string", "value": "John Doe" },
      { "type": "string", "value": "Jane Doe" },
      { "type": "string", "value": "Bob Smith" }
    ]
  },
  {
    "_id": "email",
    "dataTypes": [
